# Blushing Brunette AI

## Mission

Build the internal operating system for Blushing Brunette.

The application should help manage:

- Merchandising
- Finance
- Marketing
- Inventory
- Product Pages
- Analytics

Every feature should save time or improve decision-making.

The app is not intended to replace Shopify or accounting software.
It should sit on top of them and provide intelligence.

---

## Version 1 Goals

### Merchandising

- Product descriptions
- SEO
- Alt text
- Founder Fit
- Product readiness score

### Finance

- Daily profit
- Cash flow
- Inventory valuation
- Break-even ROAS
- Forecasting

### Marketing

- Email
- SMS
- Meta Ads
- Social captions
- UGC scripts

---

## Core Principles

- Never invent product facts.
- Verified information always wins.
- Human approval before publishing.
- Every recommendation should explain why.
